## Setmap command loc.

setmap-command-description = Sets the game to start with a given map next round.
setmap-command-help = setmap <map ID>
setmap-command-need-one-argument = setmap takes one argument, ID of the game map.
setmap-command-success = Sets the game to start with map { $map } next round.
setmap-command-arg-map = <map ID>
setmap-command-notlobby = Set map available only in lobby!
setmap-command-notlobby-time = Set map available only in lobby with { $time } remaining!
